    {
      "id": "71f4ab1e-ef61-48f3-92e8-70691f7d0750",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        480,
        180
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 606,
        "height": 264,
        "content": "## 1. 导入现有内容\n[详细了解HTML节点](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/builtin/core-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.html/)\n\n首先，我们需要收集与目标品牌声线相符的现有内容。这些内容可以是博客文章、社交媒体帖子或内部文档——其核心在于利用这些内容\"训练\"AI，使其能根据提供的范例生成新内容。需要特别注意的是，内容的质量和一致性对实现预期效果至关重要。\n\n在本演示中，我们将从企业博客中提取最新博文作为范例。由于博客文章通常因发布渠道的专业性和主题聚焦而保持较高一致性，这能很好地展示该工作流程的效果。"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "3d3a55a5-4b4a-4ea2-a39c-82b366fb81e6",
      "name": "Sticky Note1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1440,
        240
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 434,
        "height": 230,
        "content": "## 2. 将HTML转换为Markdown\n[了解更多关于Markdown节点的信息](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/builtin/core-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.markdown)\n\nMarkdown是优化发送给LLM的文章数据的绝佳方式，因为它减少了所需的标记数量，同时保留了所有相关的写作结构信息。\n\n获取Markdown格式的响应同样实用，因为这通常是作者们撰写内容时采用的格式。"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "08c0b683-ec06-47ce-871c-66265195ca29",
      "name": "Sticky Note2",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1980,
        80
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 446,
        "height": 233,
        "content": "## 3. 利用AI分析文章结构与写作风格\n[进一步了解基础LLM链节点](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/builtin/cluster-nodes/root-nodes/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainllm)\n\n我们的方法是首先对所有可用文章进行高层次分析，以复现其内容布局和写作风格。这将作为指导方针，帮助AI构建我们未来的文章框架。"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "515fe69f-061e-4dfc-94ed-4cf2fbe10b7b",
      "name": "Capture Existing Article Structure",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "position": [
        2020,
        380
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "text": "={{ $json.data.join('\\n---\\n') }}",
        "messages": {
          "messageValues": [
            {
              "message": "=Given the following one or more articles (which are separated by ---), describe how best one could replicate the common structure, layout, language and writing styles of all as aggregate."
            }
          ]
        },
        "promptType": "define"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1.4
    },
    {
      "id": "ba4e68fb-eccc-4efa-84be-c42a695dccdb",
      "name": "Markdown",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.markdown",
      "position": [
        1600,
        540
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "html": "={{ $json.data }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "d459ff5b-0375-4458-a49f-59700bb57e12",
      "name": "Sticky Note3",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        2340,
        740
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 446,
        "height": 253,
        "content": "## 4. 运用AI提取声音特征与特质\n[详细了解信息提取节点](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/builtin/cluster-nodes/root-nodes/n8n-nodes-langchain.information-extractor/)\n\n其次，我们将利用人工智能分析过往文章的品牌声音特征。通过识别文章采用的语调、风格及措辞偏好，并将其归类。这些分类将作为指导原则，确保AI生成的新文章在语气和风格上保持一致性。"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "71fe32a9-1b8a-446c-a4ff-fb98c6a68e1b",
      "name": "Sticky Note4",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        2720,
        0
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 626,
        "height": 633,
        "content": "## 5. 利用AI自动化生成品牌风格文章\n[详细了解信息提取节点](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/builtin/cluster-nodes/root-nodes/n8n-nodes-langchain.information-extractor)\n\n通过这种方法，我们最终可以将内容规范和品牌声线指南输入到大型语言模型（即内容生成代理）中，批量生产符合品牌调性的文章、社交媒体帖子等内容。\n\n需要注意的是，AI在模拟目标文章格式及复用常见短语措辞方面表现优异。但这种模式化输出极易陷入重复！虽然人工智能能显著提升创作效率，但仍需人工润色来增添文本多样性。"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "4e6fbe4e-869e-4bef-99ba-7b18740caecf",
      "name": "Content Generation Agent",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.informationExtractor",
      "position": [
        3000,
        320
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "text": "={{ $json.instruction }}",
        "options": {
          "systemPromptTemplate": "=You are a blog content writer who writes using the following article guidelines. Write a content piece as requested by the user. Output the body as Markdown. Do not include the date of the article because the publishing date is not determined yet.\n\n## Brand Article Style\n{{ $('Article Style & Brand Voice').item.json.text }}\n\n##n Brand Voice Characteristics\n\nHere are the brand voice characteristic and examples you must adopt in your piece. Pick only the characteristic which make sense for the user's request. Try to keep it as similar as possible but don't copy word for word.\n\n|characteristic|description|examples|\n|-|-|-|\n{{\n$('Article Style & Brand Voice').item.json.output.map(item => (\n`|${item.characteristic}|${item.description}|${item.examples.map(ex => `\"${ex}\"`).join(', ')}|`\n)).join('\\n')\n}}"
        },
        "attributes": {
          "attributes": [
            {
              "name": "title",
              "required": true,
              "description": "title of article"
            },
            {
              "name": "summary",
              "required": true,
              "description": "summary of article"
            },
            {
              "name": "body",
              "required": true,
              "description": "body of article"
            },
            {
              "name": "characteristics",
              "required": true,
              "description": "comma delimited string of characteristics chosen"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "022de44c-c06c-41ac-bd50-38173dae9b37",
      "name": "Sticky Note6",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        3460,
        480
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 406,
        "height": 173,
        "content": "## 6. 保存草稿至Wordpress\n[了解更多关于Wordpress节点的信息](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/builtin/app-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.wordpress/)\n\n作为模板的收尾步骤，我们将简单地把生成的文章保存为草稿，这样可以让团队成员在发布前进行人工审核和验证。"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "fe54c40e-6ddd-45d6-a938-f467e4af3f57",
      "name": "Sticky Note5",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        2900,
        660
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 440,
        "height": 120,
        "content": "### 问：每篇文章都需要分析品牌声调吗？\n答：不需要！建议将AI的分析结果存储起来，针对一系列计划发布的文章重复使用，而非每次都重新生成。"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "1832131e-21e8-44fc-9370-907f7b5a6eda",
      "name": "Sticky Note7",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        1000,
        680
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 380,
        "height": 120,
        "content": "### 问：除了博客文章，我还能使用其他媒体吗？\n答：当然可以！这种方法同样适用于PDF等其他来源材料，只要能将它们转换为文本格式提供给大语言模型即可。"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "8e8706a3-122d-436b-9206-de7a6b2f3c39",
      "name": "Sticky Note8",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -220,
        -120
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 400,
        "height": 800,
        "content": "## 试试看吧！\n### 本n8n模板演示如何通过分析已发布内容，利用AI生成符合品牌调性的新文本\n\n采用这种方法，您可以快速生成大量博客草稿，同时确保内容与品牌形象及既有作品保持高度一致。\n\n### 工作原理\n* 本演示以n8n.io博客作为现有内容源，通过HTTP节点导入最新5篇文章\n* HTML节点提取文章正文后转换为适合大语言模型的Markdown格式\n* 通过LLM节点实现：(1)解析文章结构与写作风格 (2)识别内容中的品牌声音特征\n* 最终在生成新文章时，这些分析结果将作为最终LLM节点的指导原则\n* 生成的草稿会保存至Wordpress，供编辑人员审阅或作为创作起点\n\n### 使用方法\n* 修改步骤1：更换目标博客数据源或调整现有内容获取方式\n* 调整步骤5：输入新文章创作指令。建议选择与品牌相关的主题以获得最佳效果\n\n### 需要帮助？\n加入[Discord讨论群](https://discord.com/invite/XPKeKXeB7d)或访问[官方论坛](https://community.n8n.io/)提问！\n\n祝您探索愉快！"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "1510782d-0f88-40ca-99a8-44f984022c8e",
      "name": "New Article Instruction",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
